---
title: German Pork Filet with Creamy Dijon Sauce Top recipes from HelloFresh markets around the world
description: In honor of the summer games, try this gold medal-winning recipe from HF Germany! You’ll elevate juicy seared pork filets with a velvety Dijon cream sauce that cascades luxuriously over every bite. Serve with golden brown roasted rosemary potatoes and carrots, and sprinkle with herbaceous parsley for a meal that’s fit for weeknights and special occasions too.
